<SUMMARY>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=2 -->
SUMMARY: 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
The Board proposes to amend its Practices and Procedures for Appeals and Stay Requests of Personnel Actions Allegedly
Based on Whistleblowing. This amendment extends the time limit for filing an appeal of an agency action where the appellant
first files a request for a stay of that action. This proposed change will bring the filing time in initial whistleblower
cases into line with filing times in the Board's appellate jurisdiction cases and will also have the effect of making
the Board's appellate processes more accessible to Federal employees.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

