A finding of no significant impact with respect to the environment has been made in accordance with HUD regulations
in 24 CFR part 50 that implement section 102(2)(C) of the National Environmental Policy Act of 1969 (42 U.S.C. 4332).
The Finding of No Significant Impact is available for public inspection between 7:30 a.m. and 5:30 p.m. weekdays in
the office of the Rules Docket Clerk at the above address. 
